# WinkWebHealth — Environment Variables

## Production (Docker on VPS)
Copy `.env.docker.example` to `.env` in the repo root and use with `docker compose up`.
See `DEPLOYMENT.md` for full hybrid cPanel + Docker setup.

## Local development

### API (api-mongoose/.env)
PORT=4545
DB_URL=mongodb://localhost:27017/winkwebhealth
JWT_SECRET=your-jwt-secret

# Comma-separated emails with platform super-admin access (/admin portal)
SUPER_ADMIN_EMAILS=you@yourdomain.com

# Paystack (primary — accepts PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY or PAYSTACK_SECRET)
PAYSTACK_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# USD list price → GHS at checkout (live rate fetched hourly; fallback if APIs down)
PAYSTACK_USD_TO_GHS_RATE=11.42

# Stripe (optional — shown in UI but disabled until configured)
STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_ID=price_...
STRIPE_PRO_PRICE_YEARLY_ID=price_...

# Web URL (for Stripe redirects, email links, logo in emails)
WEB_URL=http://localhost:8080

# Optional: override logo URL in emails (defaults to WEB_URL/logo.png)
# EMAIL_LOGO_URL=https://winkwebhealth.com/logo.png

### Worker (uses api-mongoose/.env or worker/.env)
DB_URL=mongodb://localhost:27017/winkwebhealth
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379

# Email alerts (SMTP)
SMTP_HOST=mail.yourdomain.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=
SMTP_FROM=alerts@winkwebhealth.com

### Web (web/.env — baked in at Docker build time)
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:4545

# Dev server runs on http://localhost:8080 (see web/vite.config.js)
